#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/logging.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"While JBoss Logging routes log messages directly to the JBoss Log Manager, one of your libraries might rely on a different logging API.\n"
"In such cases, you need to use a <<logging-apis,logging adapter>> to ensure that its log messages are routed to JBoss Log Manager as well."
msgstr "虽然 JBoss 日志系统会将日志消息直接转发到 JBoss 日志管理器，但您的某个库可能依赖于其他日志 API。在这种情况下，您需要使用 xref:logging-apis[日志适配器] ，以确保该库的日志消息也能被转发到 JBoss 日志管理器。"

