#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/logging.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "With this classic approach, you use a specific API to obtain a logger instance, store it in a static field of a class, and call logging operations upon this instance."
msgstr "采用这种经典方法，您需要使用特定的 API 获取一个日志记录器实例，将其存储在类的静态字段中，然后通过该实例调用日志记录操作。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/logging.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "The same flow can be applied with any of the <<logging-apis,supported logging APIs>>."
msgstr "该流程可适用于任何 xref:logging-apis[受支持的日志记录 API] 。"

#. type: Block title
#: _versions/main/guides/logging.adoc
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid "An example of storing a logger instance into a static field by using the JBoss Logging API:"
msgstr "以下是一个使用 JBoss 日志记录 API 将日志记录器实例存储到静态字段中的示例："

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/logging.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Define the logger field."
msgstr "定义日志记录器字段。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/logging.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Invoke the desired logging methods on the `log` object."
msgstr "在 `日志` 对象上调用所需的日志记录方法。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/logging.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "When you create a `Logger` instance, Quarkus keeps metadata associated with the `Logger` name in memory for the full lifecycle of the application."
msgstr "当您创建一个 `Logger` 实例时，Quarkus 会在应用程序的整个生命周期内，将与该 `Logger` 名称相关的元数据保存在内存中。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/logging.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Do not use an unbounded dynamic name for loggers, for example, `for (int i ...) { Logger.getLogger(\"logger-name.\" + i).info(\"my log\") }`."
msgstr "请勿为日志记录器使用未限定范围的动态名称，例如： `for (int i …​) { Logger.getLogger(\"logger-name.\" + i).info(\"my log\") }` 。"

#. type: Title ==
#: _versions/main/guides/logging.adoc
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid "Simplified logging"
msgstr "简化日志记录"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/logging.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Quarkus simplifies logging by automatically adding logger fields to classes that use `io.quarkus.logging.Log`.\n"
"This eliminates the need for repetitive boilerplate code and enhances the convenience of logging setup."
msgstr "Quarkus 通过自动向使用 `io.quarkus.logging.Log` 的类中添加日志器字段，简化了日志记录。这消除了重复的模板代码，并提高了日志配置的便捷性。"

#. type: Block title
#: _versions/main/guides/logging.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "An example of simplified logging with static method calls:"
msgstr "以下是一个使用静态方法调用进行简化日志记录的示例："

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/logging.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "The io.quarkus.logging.Log class provides the same methods as JBoss Logging, but as static methods."
msgstr "io.quarkus.logging.Log 类提供了与 JBoss Logging 相同的方法，但这些方法是静态方法。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/logging.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The class does not declare a logger field.\n"
"During the application build, Quarkus creates a `private static final org.jboss.logging.Logger` field in each class that uses the `Log` API.\n"
"Quarkus uses the fully qualified name of the calling class as the logger name.\n"
"In this example, the logger name is `com.example.MyService`."
msgstr "该类未声明日志器字段。在应用程序构建过程中，Quarkus 会在每个使用 `Log` API 的类中创建 `一个私有静态 final org.jboss.logging.Logger` 字段。 Quarkus 使用调用类的完全限定名称作为日志器名称。在此示例中，日志器名称为 `com.example.MyService` 。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/logging.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "During the application build, Quarkus rewrites calls to `Log` methods into JBoss Logging calls on the generated logger field."
msgstr "在应用程序构建过程中，Quarkus 会将对 `Log` 方法的调用重写为对生成的 logger 字段的 JBoss Logging 调用。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/logging.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Use the `Log` API only in application classes, not in external dependencies.\n"
"`Log` method calls not processed by Quarkus at build time will result in an exception."
msgstr "请仅在应用程序类中使用 `日志` API，不要在外部依赖项中使用。在构建时未由 Quarkus 处理的 `日志` 方法调用将引发异常。"

#. type: Block title
#: _versions/main/guides/logging.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Using `io.quarkus.logging.Log` in extensions:"
msgstr "在扩展中使用 `io.quarkus.logging.Log` ："

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/logging.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "While the `Log` API simplifies logging in application classes, it is not recommended for use in extension modules or external dependencies."
msgstr "虽然 `Log` API 简化了在应用程序类中进行日志记录的操作，但不建议在扩展模块或外部依赖项中使用它。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/logging.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "The following considerations apply:"
msgstr "需考虑以下几点："

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/logging.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "`io.quarkus.logging.Log` depends on Quarkus bytecode transformations that occur at build time."
msgstr "`io.quarkus.logging.Log` 依赖于构建时执行的 Quarkus 字节码转换。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/logging.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"In extension modules, `Log` works only if the module includes a Jandex index.\n"
"However, this behavior is unsupported and can lead to unreliable logging."
msgstr "在扩展模块中， `Log` 仅在该模块包含 Jandex 索引时才有效。不过，这种行为不受支持，可能会导致日志记录不可靠。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/logging.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "For extension development, use `org.jboss.logging.Logger.getLogger(String)` instead of `io.quarkus.logging.Log`."
msgstr "在开发扩展时，请使用 `org.jboss.logging.Logger.getLogger(String)` ，而不是 `io.quarkus.logging.Log` 。"

#. type: Title ==
#: _versions/main/guides/logging.adoc
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid "Injecting a configured logger"
msgstr "注入一个已配置的日志记录器"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/logging.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Instead of declaring a logger field, you can use an alternative approach and inject a configured `org.jboss.logging.Logger` instance by using `@Inject`.\n"
"This approach applies only to CDI beans."
msgstr "除了声明一个日志记录器字段外，您还可以采用另一种方法，即使用 `@Inject` 注入一个已配置的 `org.jboss.logging.Logger` 实例。此方法仅适用于 CDI Bean。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/logging.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "To control the logger name, choose one of the following injection patterns:"
msgstr "要控制日志记录器的名称，请选择以下注入模式之一："

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/logging.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Use `@Inject Logger log` when you want Quarkus to name the logger after the class it is injected into."
msgstr "当希望 Quarkus 根据被注入的类来命名日志器时，请使用 `@Inject Logger log` 。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/logging.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Use `@LoggerName(\"...\") Logger log` when you want to set the logger name explicitly."
msgstr "若需显式设置日志器名称，请使用 `@LoggerName(\"…​\") Logger log` 。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/logging.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "`@Inject` is not required if you already annotated your `Logger` with `@LoggerName(\"...\")`."
msgstr "如果您已经使用 `@LoggerName(\"…​\")` 注解了 `Logger` ，则无需使用 `@Inject` 。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/logging.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Once injected, you can use the `log` object to invoke logging methods."
msgstr "注入后，您可以使用 `日志` 对象来调用日志记录方法。"

#. type: Block title
#: _versions/main/guides/logging.adoc
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid "An example of two different types of logger injection:"
msgstr "以下是一个关于两种不同类型日志注入的示例："

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/logging.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "The logger is created with `org.jboss.logging.Logger.getLogger(SimpleBean.class)`."
msgstr "该日志器是通过 `org.jboss.logging.Logger.getLogger(SimpleBean.class)` 创建的。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/logging.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"In this case, the name \"foo\" is used as a logger name.\n"
"The logger is created with `org.jboss.logging.Logger.getLogger(\"foo\")`."
msgstr "在此示例中，名称“foo”用作日志记录器的名称。该日志记录器通过 `org.jboss.logging.Logger.getLogger(\"foo\")` 创建。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/logging.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Quarkus caches logger instances internally.\n"
"When you inject a logger into a `@RequestScoped` bean, Quarkus shares that logger across bean instances to avoid performance penalties from repeated logger instantiation."
msgstr "Quarkus 会在内部缓存日志器实例。当您将日志器注入到 `@RequestScoped 范围的` Bean 中时，Quarkus 会在各个 Bean 实例之间共享该日志器，以避免因重复实例化日志器而导致的性能开销。"

