#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/logging.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "The option is available for all handler types: `quarkus.log.console.json.mdc.flat-fields`, `quarkus.log.file.json.mdc.flat-fields`, `quarkus.log.syslog.json.mdc.flat-fields`, `quarkus.log.socket.json.mdc.flat-fields`, and named handlers such as `quarkus.log.handler.console.<name>.json.mdc.flat-fields`."
msgstr "该选项适用于所有处理程序类型： `quarkus.log.console.json.mdc.flat-fields` 、 `quarkus.log.file.json.mdc.flat-fields` 、 `quarkus.log.syslog.json.mdc.flat-fields` 、 `quarkus.log.socket.json.mdc.flat-fields` ，以及诸如 `quarkus.log.handler.console.<name>.json.mdc.flat-fields` 之类的命名处理程序。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/logging.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"*ecs*: Uses the link:https://www.elastic.co/docs/reference/ecs/ecs-field-reference[Elastic Common Schema (ECS)] format.\n"
"This format modifies some default field names and adds other fields to align with ECS."
msgstr "*ecs* ：采用 link:https://www.elastic.co/docs/reference/ecs/ecs-field-reference[弹性通用模式（ECS）] 格式。该格式对某些默认字段名称进行了修改，并添加了其他字段，以符合 ECS 规范。"

#. type: Plain text
