#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/logging.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The `JsonProvider` SPI allows you to dynamically inject additional JSON fields into every log record at formatting time.\n"
"Each registered provider's `writeTo` method is called once per log record, receiving a `JsonLogGenerator` and the `ExtLogRecord` being formatted."
msgstr "`JsonProvider` SPI 允许您在格式化时将额外的 JSON 字段动态注入到每条日志记录中。每个已注册提供程序的 `writeTo` 方法都会在每条日志记录生成时被调用一次，该方法会接收一个 `JsonLogGenerator 对象` 以及正在格式化的 `ExtLogRecord` 对象。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/logging.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Providers can inspect the log record (level, logger name, MDC values, message, etc.) to decide which fields, if any, to add.\n"
"Any keys listed in `quarkus.log.*.json.excluded-keys` are still filtered, even when written by a provider."
msgstr "提供程序可以检查日志记录（级别、日志器名称、MDC 值、消息等），以决定是否需要添加哪些字段。即使由提供程序写入 `，quarkus.log.*.json.excluded-keys` 中列出的任何键仍会被过滤。"

